{"tid":2429534,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"太極樂隊唐奕聰猝逝　鄧建明證實死訊","createTime":"2021-03-02T11:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T01:42:52.000Z","uid":212249,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e12efcf7e2080e64f454543da59568f0ee524e5b","tid":2429534,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210302/photo/bkn-20210302185410513-0302_00862_001_01p.jpg?20210302191044\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210302%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210302185410513-0302_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20210302191044&h=0122a696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太極樂隊鍵琴手唐奕聰（Gary）被指在家中昏迷不醒，疑因心臟病發猝逝，終年57歲。除了是樂隊成員之外，他亦是著名音樂監製，與已故樂壇天王張國榮合作無間。太極成員之一鄧建明（Joey Tang）向好友證實死訊。<br />\n<br />\n就此事致電Gary，其妻接聽，言談間未有否認死訊：「我依家唔方便講咁多，有好多嘢要處理，之後再聯絡你哋。」"},{"pid":"45691a94dceeae038ec799739369df2201ea165b","tid":2429534,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"東網唔貼link"},{"pid":"052d7807dd8cfe16f184b20bfaa155251d2fd8ad","tid":2429534,"uid":59538,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:21:48.000Z","msg":"Gray Tong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6540a7afea5dceede39c1d4a97b91200784ad1d7","tid":2429534,"uid":387466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:22:09.000Z","msg":"近排咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c90602f478147c43b6e93a873d65a9e7cfc2ec5","tid":2429534,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"ddc84f7d7d36fffb96cd1a11fdf8a1332a575818","tid":2429534,"uid":175079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:2